HEADWORD: Spheral
<hw>Spher"al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Of or
pertaining to a sphere or the spheres.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Rounded like a sphere; sphere-shaped; hence,
symmetrical; complete; perfect.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sphere</ent>⟦br⟧
